  "remarks": "Andrey Vorobyov is the governor of Moscow Oblast, appointed by President Vladimir Putin. In his role as governor, Andrey Vorobyov manages a regional state body of the Russian Federation and is responsible for implementing state policies at regional level. He has expressed support for the illegal recognition of the so-called independence of the so-called Donetsk and Luhansk Peoples Republics and the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
